item.title: My TED Talk To Baby Kale Today - H(you)uman
item.description: My baby kale is 7 days old and they need more personal space, so I give them a free TED Talk just to prepare them for this whole new world. In case any human need, I also post it here. In this talk, I will discuss about human problems and their solutions.
